descriptors.name: iostream_usart_baremetal
descriptors.label: Platform - I/O Stream USART Bare-metal
descriptors.description: This example project uses the I/O Stream service running in a bare-metal configuration to demonstrate the use of UART communication over the virtual COM port (VCOM). The application will echo back any characters it receives over the serial connection. The VCOM serial port can be used either over USB or by connecting to port 4902 if the kit is connected via Ethernet.
